data.description: Get ready to fall in love with this amazing 3 bed 2.5 bath house! It features a new roof installed in 2018, new carpet and flooring for a modern look, and fresh paint! With an oversized 2 car garage, you'll have plenty of space for parking and storage. Plus, this house sits on a corner lot, giving you extra privacy and room to enjoy outdoor activities. The basement has a walkout to the back yard for added convenience.
